Template provenance
-------------------
The sealed Astro template and its section library (templates/) were developed
with reference to design patterns in the HuggingFace WebSight dataset. No
WebSight dataset content is redistributed in this repository; the components
here are original, re-authored Astro/MDX. The WebSight-derived training data
and mapper tooling are NOT part of this repository.
